<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink350">
<l>avarō vārār tāṉvan taṉṟē</l>
<l>vēmpi ṉoṇpū vuṟaippat</l>
<l>tēmpaṭu kiḷaviyavar teḷikkum poḻutē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Won’t he himself come? The season has arrived, </l>
<l>when they speak honeyed words, </l>
<l>as bright flowers bloom upon the Neem tree. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
